{"tid":1717762,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"荃灣黑衣青年倒臥街頭浴血 疑高處墮下身亡","createTime":"2019-11-13T16:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T17:32:48.000Z","uid":4783,"like":34,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"de652e053c653c575894b2b9316b35920355a34c","tid":1717762,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"2019-11-13 23:56<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-11-14 00:08<br />\n<br />\n深夜10時許，有人途經荃灣嘉里物流中心對開，發現一名身穿黑衣、黑褲的青年，倒臥在地面浴血，昏迷不醒，立即報案求助。救護員趕到現場，為傷者作初步檢查，發現他身體多處受傷，需急送就近的仁濟醫院，經搶救後延至深夜約11時許證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n據知，最初有人以為黑衫青年被人斬傷，但有消息稱，依據傷者傷勢所見，懷疑是從高處墮下所致。警方指，晚上10時37分，警方接報荃灣嘉利物流中心對開，有人報案指，一名男子倒地昏迷不醒，口部有流血，救護員到場將男子送往醫院救治，案件列作「受傷人發現」跟進。<br />\n<br />\nsource hk01唔貼"},{"pid":"7e3b51e4e6e7c2eb08d3c551f537c084e725f7fd","tid":1717762,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de404e51417ca45725e1a19ae5e165f794931c0","tid":1717762,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"Oh diu"},{"pid":"151963c86c9130a045a0a4266e0696faea6a207e","tid":1717762,"uid":36182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"又一個...."},{"pid":"70647f60b7b0d8cf5a93f82de6e9c360846b9387","tid":1717762,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c636d69e0036468f213dedee5bb10cbe931dd4","tid":1717762,"uid":21782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,